2016-12-19T16:12:50.000Z","msg":"一心諗住睇甜故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f519e64133cd5717abedb5e14cbe77d3a7253544","tid":46400,"uid":30814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:17:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一心諗住睇甜故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n甜左嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ac11b56ca9c9c10f1b65babd951bb5508732af1","tid":46400,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:17:46.000Z","msg":"今次我醒目，先叫我女友用皮帶綁他雙手，再去到他前面，想幫佢插我女友。<br />\n<br />\n在我走到他前面時，將手放到他肩膀上時，忽然雙腳一痛，倒在床上。<br />\n<br />\n呀呀呀呀呀呀呀呀呀呀呀!!!!!!<br />\n好撚痛呀！突然屎眼一痛。仆街，佢踢我呀!!佢又壓上來啦，佢又插錯洞呀!!!<br />\n<br />\n我流著血又流著淚說:<br />\nTerry哥，你想點呀，又入晒啦。<br />\n<br />\nTerry抱歉的說道：<br />\n對唔住，其實我是職業的摔角，但又學過幾年柔道，一個學過柔道的人有咁既自然也好正常的，插錯，唔好意思。<br />\n<br />\n今次我無出聲了，默默咁唔知抽插多幾吓先拔出來，我放棄了。<br />\n而且，我女友真係出晒水，不過係笑到出眼水&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2af848b02be2c28aa68566a233a3edb04e641195","tid":46400,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:20:19.000Z","msg":"應該還有幾個post，想快速爛尾，我最喜歡爛尾。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd7a98d98ff8db4ba6041b396a94a992ed9c2d36","tid":46400,"uid":8000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:21:12.000Z","msg":"睇緊<br />\n長d會好d<br />\n幾好"},{"pid":"30b445e246e10ca5c493e3fc61c88131e8dbff0e","tid":46400,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:26:29.000Z","msg":"過左三日後，<br />\n如今屎眼還是隱隱作痛以後...<br />\n<br />\n女朋友關心道：<br />\nBB，好返啲未呀，對唔住呀，Terry無心的。<br />\n<br />\n我生氣的說：<br />\n無心以經搞到我爛晒，有心我直頭可以拳頭入菊花啦!<br />\n<br />\n女友說:<br />\n最多下次找個TB比你玩3p啦，雖然我接受唔到女人掂你，但TB我還可以忍受。<br />\n<br />\n我立刻喜道：<br />\n唔痛了，幾時，依家都得。<br />\n<br />\n一日後&hellip;3p要開始了，我好興奮，我好興奮。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9a68ff5aa090ad0bdecdd1aea0b8d180df1bb10","tid":46400,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:33:44.000Z","msg":"一日後，我在家裡等我女友帶TB回來，仲以經為我屎眼搽咗金創藥。一心準備玩3p。<br />\n<br />\n一開門，我又見到女友帶了Terry回來。<br />\n<br />\n我激動地說：<br />\n仆街，點解又係你!!!TB呢!!!<br />\n<br />\n女友微笑的說道:<br />\n其實他全名叫Terrybaby，我地朋友都叫佢做TB。<br />\n之後佢地關上門，仲反鎖!!<br />\n結果係點，我估我唔駛多講&hellip;.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又過左三日.."},{"pid":"9ab50bf033745706abbd073cf38fafab9c600e37","tid":46400,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:38:54.000Z","msg":"三日裡，我已哭光眼淚流光血，我唔知做錯啲乜女友咁玩我。<br />\n我哭著的問：<br />\n點解妳要玩我&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n女友冷笑回答到:<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無鬼用，叫Admin開個癡線佬台比你咁耐到冇，當然要罰吓你啦，廢柴。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAdmin開個癡線佬台比我。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf63f9748a797020e05f74d71e9304c73f61865f","tid":46400,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:40:04.000Z","msg":"完啦，講完故果然會眼訓，希望唔會發惡夢啦。<br />\n各位，早抖。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f1a7fbcd32c9e62743f6534ebe5374759ecf2a3","tid":46400,"uid":39207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:41:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8f38e252a0f70a4486af2f1a81dd340e1d9fbbee","tid":46400,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:44:23.000Z","msg":"其實仲有少少諗到無寫，不過剛好眼訓，所以快速爛尾。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57b438d5f8a927c736278d5b004e7b947a212596","tid":46400,"uid":9483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:44:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0513523e1912a6c3a0ee16cdb19ba3e3